kconfgen
========

.. image:: https://secure.travis-ci.org/rbarrois/kconfgen.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/rbarrois/kconfgen/

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/kconfgen.svg
